And by and by
they considered Ella

357
00:21:40,024 --> 00:21:43,503
less a sister than a servant.

358
00:21:44,890 --> 00:21:48,143
And so Ella was left
to do all the work.

359
00:21:49,657 --> 00:21:51,641
This was a good thing,

360
00:21:51,666 --> 00:21:53,960
for it distracted her
from her grief.

361
00:21:53,985 --> 00:21:57,011
At least that was what
her stepmother said.

362
00:21:58,391 --> 00:22:01,725
And she and her two daughters
were more than happy

363
00:22:01,758 --> 00:22:06,832
to provide Ella with lots
and lots of distraction.

364
00:22:12,992 --> 00:22:17,512
In their defense, they did share
with her the very food they ate,

365
00:22:17,537 --> 00:22:21,215
or rather,
the scraps from their table.

366
00:22:21,559 --> 00:22:23,705
She had little
in the way of friends.

367
00:22:23,730 --> 00:22:26,541
Well, her friends
were very little.

